OL,3,CMan jailed for driving deliberately at
OL,4,Cvictim causing him to have leg
OL,5,Camputated
OL,7,FThe driver of a Range Rover has been
OL,8,Fjailed for 13 years and six months for
OL,9,Fdriving 'deliberately' at an innocent
OL,10,Fmember of the public in Bournemouth
OL,11,Fand 'pinning him against a wall',
OL,12,Fcausing him to have his leg amputated.
OL,14,FVinny Dean Conrad Morgan, 21, was
OL,15,Ffound guilty of grievous bodily harm
OL,16,Fwith intent, conspiracy to commit
OL,17,Faffray and possession of an offensive
OL,18,Fweapon.
