OL,7,FHis father, Conrad Lee Morgan, 55, of
OL,8,FBournemouth, was also found guilty of
OL,9,Fconspiracy to commit affray and
OL,10,Fpossession of an offensive weapon.
OL,12,FA Dorset Police spokesman said that
OL,13,Fthe two defendants had been in
OL,14,Fpossession of baseball bats and
OL,15,Finvolved in an altercation with two
OL,16,Fother men in Etches Close,
OL,17,FBournemouth, on October 7 2024.
