OL,3,CMan jailed for driving deliberately at
OL,4,Cvictim causing him to have leg
OL,5,Camputated
OL,7,FHe said: "The victim went to assist
OL,8,Fthe men and as he was doing so, the
OL,9,FRange Rover returned to the scene and
OL,10,Fdrove directly at him.
OL,12,F"He initially jumped out of the way,
OL,13,Fbut the vehicle reversed and drove at
OL,14,Fhim again, pinning him against a wall.
OL,16,F"The Range Rover was then turned round
OL,17,Fand left the scene.
OL,19,F"The defendants were arrested during
OL,20,Fthe early hours of the next morning
OL,21,Ffollowing enquiries by officers."
