OL,5,Camputated
OL,7,FHe added: "Emergency services attended
OL,8,Fand the man, aged in his 20s, was
OL,9,Ftaken to hospital for treatment to a
OL,10,Fserious injury to his left leg, which
OL,11,Fsubsequently required amputation."
OL,13,FVinny Morgan was jailed for a total of
OL,14,F13 years and six months and was banned
OL,15,Ffrom driving for 10 years and nine
OL,16,Fmonths, while Conrad Morgan received a
OL,17,Fprison sentence of nine months.
