OL,7,FDetective Sergeant Sarah Hodgson said:
OL,8,F"This was a shockingly violent and
OL,9,Fdangerous act involving a vehicle
OL,10,Fdeliberately being driven at an
OL,11,Finnocent member of the public.
OL,13,F"The victim has suffered a horrendous
OL,14,Finjury as a result, however, the
OL,15,Factions of these defendants could
OL,16,Feasily have resulted in a fatality."
